   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sc080a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">Knoxville</name>
                     <date when="1812-11-16">Nov. 16th 1812</date>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <salute>Sir,</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Our desire, to bring to a close, the lottery, for the benefit of East Tennessee College, induces us, to solicit, that you will, as soon as possible, have your account settled, by returning the Tickets you received, or rewriting to us the amount of the money, for which you may have sold. <add place="left of salute">
                  <hi rend="different hand">50 tickets }</hi>
               </add>
            </p>
            <closer>
               <salute>By order of the Trustees</salute>
               <signed>
                  <name type="person">Hugh White</name>
                  <unclear>ch</unclear>
               </signed>
               <add>Included the 50 above mentioned tickets to <name type="person">Hugh L White</name>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Esq</abbr>
                     <expan>Esquire</expan>
                  </choice> by mail <date when="1812-11-30">30th Nov. 1812</date>
                  <name type="person">
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Wm</abbr>
                        <expan>William</expan>
                     </choice> Cage</name>
               </add>
               <pb n="2" facs="sc080b.small.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>The Honorable</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="person">Hugh L White</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">Knoxville</name>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <pb n="3" facs="sc080c.small.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Messrs.</abbr>
                        <expan>Messieurs</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <name type="person">Winchester &amp; Cage</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Merchants <name type="place">Cairo</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Ten</abbr>
                        <expan>Tennessee</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <add place="above address on left">
                  <name type="place">Knoxville</name>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Ten</abbr>
                     <expan>Tennessee</expan>
                  </choice>
                  <lb/>
                  <date when="--11-21">21 November</date> } </add>
               <add place="above address on right">Paid 17</add>
               <add place="bottom left corner of page, sideways">
                  <name type="person">Hugh L White</name>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Esqr</abbr>
                     <expan>Esquire</expan>
                  </choice>
                  <lb/>
                  <date when="1812-11-16">16th Nov. 1812</date>
                  <lb/> concerning lottery <lb/> tickets</add>
            </closer>
         </div>
